node.text: For or anyone who would rather stay home to shop like me, @Amazon is your one-stop-shop for anything you need for back to school this year— everything from home decor for your study space to traditional school supplies like this sweet faux leather journal. #ad Also think it’s worth mentioning that if you sign up with your parent for an #AmazonTeen login, you can browse from the privacy of your own profile that is linked to your parent’s account and credit card. Click the link in my bio to start shopping some of my Amazon favorites! You can watch my stories to learn more #happyschoolyear

node.text: June is National Acne Awareness Month so I wanted to share two products that I consistently use within my routine to keep my skin clear. I have been using the @neutrogena Oil-Free Acne Wash Pink Grapefruit collection for years! This facial cleanser removes oil and dirt that can clog pores with 2% Salicylic Acid, yet rinses clean without over-drying. The Body Clear Body Wash Pink Grapefruit is perfect to clear and help prevent any body acne. Bonus: they both smell amazing! #NTGspokesperson
